---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="About Us"
    description="Learn about the Wayfarers Alumni Association"
>
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">
                About Wayfarers Alumni
            </h1>

            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center mb-12">
                    Wayfarers Alumni is the alumni group of the Wayfarers Hiking
                    Society, part of the University of Birmingham Guild of
                    Students.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                    Our Connection to the Society
                </h2>
                <p>
                    While we are proud to have our roots in the Wayfarers Hiking
                    Society, the alumni group operates independently from the
                    society, the University of Birmingham, and the Guild of
                    Students. We maintain our own organization, activities, and
                    community, though we occasionally link together with the
                    society for certain trips and events.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    Our mission is to preserve the camaraderie and spirit of
                    adventure that defined our time as members of the Wayfarers
                    Hiking Society. We aim to:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Connect alumni from all graduation years</li>
                    <li>Organize reunions, social events, and group hikes</li>
                    <li>Share trip reports and photos from our adventures</li>
                    <li>Support the next generation of Wayfarers hikers</li>
                    <li>Maintain lifelong friendships forged on the trails</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our History</h2>
                <p>
                    The Wayfarers Hiking Society has been taking students on
                    adventures through the British countryside for decades. As
                    members graduated and moved on to new chapters of their
                    lives, the need to maintain those connections became clear.
                    The Wayfarers Alumni was established to ensure that the
                    friendships made and memories created during university
                    years would endure beyond graduation.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Join Our Community</h2>
                <p>
                    Whether you graduated last year or thirty years ago, you are
                    always a part of the Wayfarers family. We welcome all alumni
                    to join our community, attend our events, and share their
                    adventures with us.
                </p>

                <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Get in Touch</h3>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        Have questions about Wayfarers Alumni? Want to learn
                        more about upcoming events? We'd love to hear from you!
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="mailto:wayfarersalumni@gmail.com"
                        class="inline-flex items-center text-green-700 hover:text-green-800 font-medium"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                        wayfarersalumni@gmail.com
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
